rth</a><sup>2</sup></li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Janos_Slynt\" title=\"Janos Slynt\">Janos Slynt</a> (?–299)</li>\n<li>Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Jacelyn_Bywater\" title=\"Jacelyn Bywater\">Jacelyn Bywater</a> (299)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Addam_Marbrand\" title=\"Addam Marbrand\">Addam Marbrand</a> (299–300)</li>\n<li>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Osfryd_Kettleblack\" title=\"Osfryd Kettleblack\">Osfryd Kettleblack</a> (300)</li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Humfrey_Waters\" title=\"Humfrey Waters\">Humfrey Waters</a> (300—)</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr><tr style=\"height:2px;\"><td></td></tr><tr><td class=\"navbox-abovebelow\" style=\";\" colspan=\"2\"><div>\n<ul><li><sup>1</sup> He died nine days after his predecessor.</li>\n<li><sup>2</sup> Manly served around the time of <a href=\"/index.php/Robert%27s_Rebellion\" title=\"Robert&#39;s Rebellion\">Robert's Rebellion</a>.</li></ul>\n</div></td></tr></tbody></table></td></tr></tbody></table>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403155421\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.168 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.685 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 1256/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 20500/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 17412/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 4728/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 17/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 1077/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.330/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.47 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  660.037      1 -total\n 74.61%  492.481      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 74.24%  490.028      1 Template:Infobox\n 15.37%  101.461      1 Template:S-bef\n 14.48%   95.605      3 Template:Main_other\n 13.17%   86.920      1 Template:S-bef/check\n 10.02%   66.158     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  4.11%   27.148      1 Template:S-ttl\n  3.09% 